usage: uselect [-h] [-s SELECT] [-i] [-m MESSAGE]

uselect is an interactive line filter intended for use in pipelines. Selected
input lines are written to stdout.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s SELECT, --select-regex SELECT
                        select lines matching regex SELECT
  -i, --invert-selection
                        select lines NOT matching regex SELECT
  -m MESSAGE, --message MESSAGE
                        message to display in status bar

https://github.com/sdt/uselect
